game.name: Pou Girl Dress Up
game.description:
This time you will find a unique character to dress up! Hey, you are going to meet a Pou girl who has a plan to go on a wonderful party! She wants to look awesome and needs your help to be the most glamorous girl at the party. You have already worked as a fashion stylist, so you know how to design a perfect outfit for anyone. Make sure to browse through a wide collection of beautiful clothes to make a firm decision in Pou Girl Dress Up game. 
  
It is surely a proud moment to play the role of a fashion advisor in this brand new dressing game for girls. Choose a nice hairstyle from different six options! Give her a nice makeover and a lovely outfit to make her look shining! Select a nice outfit and then combine her with a matching hat and specs to complete her look for the party! Do your best to find out the cutest look for this unique girl! 

Pou girl is different from the real girl, so she follows a unique special style. You have to go through all the six options to make her look pretty. Each category has six different options to choose from. We are delighted to offer a wider collection of girls games online that you can explore in multiple devices, and require no download. Choose your game and start making the best out of the online gaming world!
